{"id": "1493696987269300234", "channel_id": "1493696987269300234", "author_id": "193043069275209728", "author_name": "princess.goth", "content": "Could we get a server rule prohibiting AI Artwork or other AI Content?\n\nJust recently it was acknowledged that the community as a whole is putting in a lot of effort to elevate the game. With Guides, Fanart or even Memes we show our passion when it comes to Morimens and its characters.\n\nSome people using AI to cheaply replicate things that others put in real effort is quite discouraging and should be actively not endorsed by the staff/server.\n\nMorimens already has a negative image with its past usages of AI so players seeing that AI is still very present in the community will definetly not help that impression of the game.\n\nPlease value the creative human effort of your community 💜", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T19:38:33.313000+00:00", "thread_id": "1493696987269300234", "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 6}, {"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}]}
